title: Will ‘Million Militia March’ Try To Stop Biden’s Inauguration?
subtitle: Given the tumultuous 2020 election season, some unrest is expected.
author: Nur Ibrahim
vclaim: On Jan. 20, 2021, millions of people will gather for the "Million Militia March"  in Washington, D.C., hoping to prevent U.S. President-elect Joe Biden’s inauguration, and to protect the capital and national monuments against “proven-violent Leftist insurgents.”
